    "sections": [
      {
        "trade": "Protection & Site Prep",
        "lines": [
          "Cover working areas: all windows, trees, bushes, plants, patio, furniture.",
          "Power wash the house.",
          "Prepare 4\"-6\" trench around the exterior walls where cracks reach grade (where possible)."
        ]
      },
      {
        "trade": "Stucco Crack Repair (Patch)",
        "lines": [
          "Scrape damaged stucco surface at crack locations.",
          "Open all cracks wider.",
          "Fix cracks and patch walls as needed.",
          "Prepare walls (brown coat, cement) at patched areas.",
          "Apply new color coat stucco to patched areas; color and texture to match existing, selected by customer.",
          "Apply caulking and bondo as needed.",
          "Seal all openings and seal around windows and doors.",
          "Clean up and haul away debris."
        ]
      },
      {
        "trade": "Wood Trim Repair",
        "lines": [
          "Sand all wood around the house.",
          "Sand the trim: fascia board, eaves, molding around windows, door frames.",
          "Patch all wood as needed.",
          "Replace damaged wood (quantity and location to be confirmed with customer)."
        ]
      },
      {
        "trade": "Exterior Paint",
        "lines": [
          "Mask all windows and doors.",
          "Customer to select paint colors and brand (Benjamin Moore, Sherwin-Williams, Dunn-Edwards, Behr or other customer preference).",
          "Apply primer to all stucco walls and trim.",
          "Apply paint to all stucco walls.",
          "Paint trim: fascia board, eaves, molding around windows, door frames."
        ]
      },
      {
        "trade": "Clean Up",
        "lines": [
          "Cover back the trench around the house.",
          "Remove all plastics and paper.",
          "Clean up and haul away debris.",
          "Clean job site."
        ]
      }
    ],
    "notes": [
      "House built in 1965 (pre-1978): exterior surfaces likely contain lead-based paint. Lead-safe scraping/sanding containment practices recommended; confirm with customer whether testing is required.",
      "Extent and location of stucco cracks not itemized by customer — estimator to walk the site and confirm crack count/locations, and whether any reach grade (trench needed) before finalizing scope."
